import ipaddress

def is_ip_in_range(ip, start_ip, end_ip):
    ip_obj = ipaddress.ip_address(ip)
    start_ip_obj = ipaddress.ip_address(start_ip)
    end_ip_obj = ipaddress.ip_address(end_ip)
    return start_ip_obj < ip_obj <= end_ip_obj
